      "creatureType": "",
      "blurb": "",
      "publicNotes": "<h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p><strong>Role:</strong> the castle's elite garrison — <strong>26 in all</strong>: 12 bunking in the barracks (A30/A38, 4 present in each at a time), 5 in the gatehouse gallery (A54), 3 before the throne (A52), and one 4-guard patrol each on the second and third floors (10% chance per 5 minutes, clockwise through unlocked rooms). Patrols matter as <em>alarm-raisers</em>: they reinforce in 1d4 rounds and scream the castle awake. After Sabina defects, @UUID[Compendium.cotct-pf2e-conversion.cotct-actors.Actor.ch6VavanaDhatri1]{Vavana Dhatri} — the Arbiter of Allegiance — commands them; Sabina's Word can still some; the rest die for the Crown.</p>",
